    public abstract class IteratingXmlRuleProvider<PAYLOADTYPE extends XmlFileModel>
extends IteratingRuleProvider<PAYLOADTYPE>
    This provides a simplified way to extend AbstractRuleProvider for cases where the rule simply needs to provide some query, and wants to execute a function over each valid xml row.
